Italiafor the first time this year, but afteran extremely bad crash in the Spring Classics,that idea was scrapped and he instead opted to do the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday Van Aert played an instrumental support role for Belgian teammate and Olympic gold medallistRemco Evenepoelafter taking a bronze in the men's time trial the week before.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 762, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5441450379350367, \"rank\": 0.8374286958534589, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel is expected to take several weeks off but Van Aert will soon be focussing again on Grand Tour stage racing.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Holiday?\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, in two weeks I will be at the start of the Vuelta\\\" Van Aert, said in the'Paris by night'Belgian television programme late on Saturday.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Aert rode for Jonas Vingegaard at the Tour de France, with a certain amount of freedom to target stages and sprints.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Vingegaard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonas Vingegaard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Vingegaard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Vingegaard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Vuelta a Espa\\u00f1a, Van Aert will race alongside another defending champion, American teammate Sepp Kuss and perha